title.rendered: Health Camp conducted for students at Mission Education centre

content.rendered: The Mission Education centre, Gramin Vikas Samiti conducted a general health checkup camp on 26th and 27th December, 2016, wherein 200 students went through the general health checkup under Dr. Krishna Kumar. Some medicines were distributed to students like Vitamin D tablets and cold syrup according to their problems. Health and Hygiene session was conducted by the doctor whereas soap, tooth paste and tooth brush was distributed to all the students.
